{"tid":2031941,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"韓正會見港區政協委員：中央立港版國安法是慎重決定","createTime":"2020-05-23T18:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T22:16:28.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"31d664c156f296d876461abd79d3ed91ffec631b","tid":2031941,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:13:24.000Z","msg":"自北京方面消息，主管港澳事務的中國國務院副總理韓正5月23日於聯組會議上接見了港區全國政協委員，並發表講話。據悉，此次會面長約1個半小時。韓正在會上指出，去年的反修例風波暴露了國安漏洞的短板，中央於去年四中全會已經下定決心，要建立香港的維護國家安全制度。他稱，香港《基本法》23條一直未落實，全球亦沒有一個國家沒有國家安全法，故這是事在必行。"},{"pid":"b78de46b33e520cb69f0278e079271e49b9fa5e5","tid":2031941,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:16:33.000Z","msg":"我知吖！大煉鋼、文革都一樣係「慎重快定」。"},{"pid":"ebf3253347982c00ec41c1fcf520122a94a2932b","tid":2031941,"uid":103156,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b78de46b33e520cb69f0278e079271e49b9fa5e5","tid":2031941,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:16:33.000Z","msg":"我知吖！大煉鋼、文革都一樣係「慎重快定」。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:16:55.000Z","msg":"決定」。"},{"pid":"148a22c09e0b3bde23a12666cbd6848521b2b235","tid":2031941,"uid":19126,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:17:28.000Z","msg":"哂鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2490bdc7d35464709788b468c64cf63b2c00199","tid":2031941,"uid":51920,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:18:00.000Z","msg":"香港公安法"},{"pid":"691d8ffe91d4ba2524c32bd0b48820d22abc7048","tid":2031941,"uid":310700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:18:03.000Z","msg":"科學決定，屌你老母啦，你老母做雞咋"},{"pid":"31a5dfe1b5bd2008aecd1422257a820c0d97c7f5","tid":2031941,"uid":35580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-23T18:18:07.000Z","msg":"